{
 "name": "RPlog_Rehab_Discovery",
 "title": "Rehab Discovery",
 "summary": "At Remembrance Hospital on Ord Mantell, Luke Skywalker visits the convalescing singer Serenella Jordain, recovering in the rehabilitation wing after a battle and a brush with spice, finding the pilot Raxis already at her bedside. As they talk, the conversation turns to Serenella's ex-husband, the dancer-turned-Sith Antoine Dareus, and Luke goes cold: he reveals he has seen Dareus alive no less than a month ago, despite Serenella's belief that he died. The discovery -- that the Sith may have brainwashed or resurrected Dareus -- shakes them all, and Serenella anxiously asks whether someone twisted by the Sith can be turned back. Luke promises to find out what he can, urging Serenella and Raxis to surround themselves with trusted friends as he takes his leave.",
